content: I've only been playing mandolin for a few weeks, and I've had this app for about the last two weeks, and it's been a fantastic tool for learning chords on the mandolin. I've played guitar for years, and when I want some chords to mandolin, I just check with the app and I'm good to go! Would recommend it to any beginner, and can see it being really useful to experts.

Chord Cracker's clear and user-friendly interface made chord analysis quite easy and actually fun! I believe beginners, like myself, will appreciate the tab function, and the ease in finding notes, chords, etc on this app. The best feature for me was how easy it is to find chords I want and then apply that to my mandolin!  More accomplished players may analyze their scale, key, and alternate tunings to make the most of this app and their instrument!
replyContent: Thank you for your comments, your support is very much appreciated by independent app developers like us!
